<br>
Consider what spell trades are worth in Kunark, also monk weapons and other armors.  10kPP is a lot of money, however you can acquire trade items that would hopefully get you said armor.<br>
<br>
Then again, I've been trying off and on to get trance sticks for a week with no luck.  Maybe all the neat Kunark stuff is just ending up on twinks... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/uafura.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Afura</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(8/25/00 12:45:43 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://wowrath.tripod.com/afura.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: True, Thog.</span><hr size=1> Just remember, there has only been 1 helm to drop on Brell... HELM.  agh  /cry  There are very very few pieces going around, and yeah, it's lore, but not no drop, but it's the fact that there's very few boots/bracers/etc, let alone BP's and that such, which are slim to nill on even exsisting on Brell.<br>
